TrafiKoro (Koropendora/?)
Monster Rancher Metropolis: Monster Rancher 4 Archive (PS2): CD/DVD/Game List: Koropendora: TrafiKoro (Koropendora/?)
By Lisa Shock on Wednesday, March 3, 2004 - 01:36 pm:

Washed and Dried: Laundry Service, LIMITED EDITION by Shakira

This is a 2-disc set, with a paper sleeve over the plastic CD case. The photo on the cover of the paper sleeve is Shakira sitting in a corner, holding a guitar. Disc 1 (Laundry Service) has 16 tracks (the last 3 are bonus material exclusive to this set) and Disc 2 (Washed and Dried) is a DVD with 3 features: Objection (live from MTV's 2002 VMAs), MTV's making of Objection, and Objection (video).
